  <releases>
    <release version="1.0.0" date="2025-06-10">
      <description>
        <p>Initial release of Assistant, your AI-powered desktop companion!</p>
        <p>Assistant allows you to interact with your Linux desktop using natural language. Chat with a local AI, execute system commands, open websites, and more, all from a GTK 4 interface. Powered by local Ollama models, Assistant works completely offline.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Initial release.</li>
          <li>Local AI chat capabilities using Ollama.</li>
          <li>Execute system commands via natural language.</li>
          <li>Smart argument extraction for commands (e.g., "open example.com").</li>
          <li>Modern GTK 4 / Adwaita user interface.</li>
          <li>Fully offline functionality—no cloud dependency.</li>
          <li>Flatpak support for easy installation.</li>
          <li>Utilizes `nomic-embed-text` for command understanding and models like `phi:2.7b-chat` for chat and argument generation.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
  </releases>

</component>
